{
  "stem": "1550.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was the situation where the men were in the men's camp, the women were in the women's camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "No, there were many, many, married couples with children and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they didn't like what was going on in these tents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not very nice, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So our-- our-- our leaders said, look, it's your fault.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Something has to be done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So various things were proposed, a camp for married people only and another camp for unmarried men and the third camp for unmarried women.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was rejected, because we had now two camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, we had to go to three camps and people are even more separated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then eventually, what came-- what was-- was finally agreed on between our-- our people and-- and the camp commandant was as follows.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Since the men's camp was a prison where every man had a cell-- which was, you could close the door.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The cell doors were not locked, by the way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't leave the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But within the camp, you were free to do whatever you want, all right?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, actually, every man had their privacy, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So what was done was that those women who were married and who had a husband in the camp, they got a passport for only certain hours during the day.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But never during the night, because it is indecent to stay with your husband during the night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's indecent.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You can only do that during the day-- during daylight hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So during the day, they were allowed to visit the men's camp and visit-- they had to go back-- these-- these times changed from time to time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were eventually extended I think until about 10:00 in the evening, but never more than that and never overnight.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
